vote.title: Authorize a twelve-month annual funding agreement with the Dallas Arboretum and Botanical Society, Inc. to provide services and program support within the city of Dallas for the period January 1, 2026 through December 31, 2026 - Not to exceed $411,000.00 - Financing: General Fund
